JD_KeMuYuE_List.利息: select  sum(Actual)  from JD_KeMuYuE_List as list inner join JD_KeMuYuE_Head as head on list.HeadUniqueNo=head.UniqueNo where Year = '2019' AND Month='8' and DptCode = 'CW10D' and (CaiWuBasicCode in ('CW30'))

JD_KeMuYuE_List.汇兑损益: select  sum(Actual)  from JD_KeMuYuE_List as list  inner join JD_KeMuYuE_Head as head on list.HeadUniqueNo=head.UniqueNo where Year = '2019' AND Month='8' and StationCode='SHANGHAI' and DptCode = 'CW10D' and (CaiWuBasicCode in ('CW40','CW50'))
